{"article_id":"B8y4g0T301GAmu1v","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former national security adviser Michael Flynn brought the investigation of Russian interference in the 2016 election to President Trump 's inner circle on Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"promising to give prosecutors information about other senior aides","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"as he pleaded guilty to a charge","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"of lying to the FBI .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Flynn ' s abrupt guilty plea is the dramatic culmination of an investigation","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Trump had once asked the FBI to drop .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"His cooperation means a top adviser in the campaign and the early days of his presidency is now providing evidence in an investigation","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that has cast a shadow over the president 's first year in office .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"And it suggests","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that the investigation remains far from over .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Flynn is the fourth former Trump aide","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to face criminal charges in special counsel Robert Mueller ' s probe of Russian interference in the 2016 presidential election ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"but the first","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to be prosecuted for things","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that happened during the Trump administration","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and the first","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to so directly bring the special counsel 's case to the administration 's door .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"In court Friday morning , prosecutors","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"prosecutors offered their first hint of the information","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Flynn might provide ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that conversations","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he had with Russia 's U.S. ambassador","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"had been coordinated by a `` senior official of the presidential transition . ''","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"In a court filing","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"made public Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"prosecutors alleged","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that Flynn \" did willfully and knowingly make materially false , fictitious and fraudulent statements \" to FBI agents during an interview on Jan. 24","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"-- four days after he began serving in the White House --","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"about his conversations with Russian ambassador Sergey Kislyak in the weeks","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"before Trump took office .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Prosecutors charged","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that he falsely told FBI agents","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that he did not ask Kislyak to delay a vote on a pending United Nations Security Council resolution","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"critical of Israeli settlements .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"That call ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"prosecutors said ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"was made at the direction of a `` very senior member of the Presidential Transition Team . ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Prosecutors did not identify the official ;","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the Associated Press and NBC News reported","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that it was Trump 's son-in-law Jared Kushner ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"citing unnamed officials .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Kushner 's lawyer could not be reached","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to comment on Friday .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Full text :","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Here is what Michael Flynn is pleading guilty to","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Prosecutors also charged","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that Flynn lied to agents about a Dec. 29 conversation","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"about how Russia might respond to sanctions","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"the U.S. government had levied over its election meddling .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"President Obama imposed those sanctions Dec. 28 ;","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"the same day , Kislyak contacted Flynn","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to discuss","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"how the Russian government would respond .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"The next day , Flynn called a `` senior official of the Presidential Transition Team '' at Trump 's private Mar-a-Lago resort ``","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to discuss what , if anything , to communicate to the Russian Ambassador about the U.S. sanctions , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"according to a court filing","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"signed by Flynn and prosecutors .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Immediately after that call , Flynn called Kislyak","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and asked","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"that Russia `` not escalate the situation . ''","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin said the following day","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that his government would not retaliate for the sanctions .","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Trump praised Putin 's move on Twitter ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"writing","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"`` I always knew","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"he was very smart ! ''","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"While incoming presidents traditionally have calls with world leaders during the transition ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"it is unusual for his aides to begin conducting foreign policy of any kind before the inauguration .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"After pleading guilty ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Flynn issued a personal statement","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that said ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` I recognize","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that the actions","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"I acknowledged in court today","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"were wrong ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"and , through my faith in God , I am working to set things right .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"My guilty plea and agreement","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"to cooperate with the Special Counsel 's Office reflect a decision","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"I made in the best interests of my family and of our country . ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"More :","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Flynn , Trump lawyers no longer sharing information on Mueller probe","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"More :","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Mueller 's bombshell :","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Special counsel charges Manafort , Gates","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and reveals aide 's Russia contacts","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"More :","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Michael Flynn faces legal peril in Washington .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"In his Rhode Island hometown , he 's revered .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Flynn , a former Army general and intelligence agency head was widely known to have been under scrutiny over his contacts with Russian officials","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"before Trump assumed the presidency .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"He also had faced scrutiny over his business dealings ,","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"including $ 530,000 in earnings from a Dutch firm with ties to the Turkish government , and payment for his 2015 Moscow speech .","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"Flynn had not registered as a foreign agent","depth":17},{"id":96,"text":"- a legal requirement -","depth":17},{"id":97,"text":"when he accepted money from the Dutch company","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"and only disclosed the payments","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"after registering retroactively amid news reports of the failing .","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"Flynn ' s attorney has maintained","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"that his client had \" fully \" informed the Defense Department of his trip to Russia .","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"He registered with the Justice Department","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"after he was ousted from the Trump administration .","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"Flynn acknowledged in a court filing","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"that his filing was `` materially false , ''","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"though prosecutors did not charge him for it .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"The administration quickly sought to distance itself from its former national security adviser on Friday .","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"In a statement , White House lawyer Ty Cobb described the former Trump confidante as `` a former National Security Adviser at the White House for 25 days and a former Obama administration official . ''","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Nothing about Flynn 's guilty plea ,","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"he said ,","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"`` implicates anyone other than Mr . Flynn . ''","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"Flynn headed the Defense Intelligence Agency under Obama while a three-star Army general .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"But in a court filing , prosecutors went out of their way","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"to highlight the former general 's close connection to Trump ,","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"pointing out","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"that he served as a `` surrogate and national security adviser '' for his campaign and a `` senior member '' of his transition team","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"before becoming his top national security aide as president .","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"Trump abruptly canceled a planned press event Friday .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"Reporters","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"assembled just outside the Oval Office for a photo opportunity with Trump and the Libyan Prime Minister Fayez al-Sarraj","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"were told to return to the briefing room .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"Democratic lawmakers seized on Flynn 's deal Friday .","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"Sen. Mark Warner , D-Va. , the ranking member of the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"that is conducting its own review of Russian meddling","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"means","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"Mueller `` has found illegal behavior","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"stretching into the senior most levels of the White House . ''","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , the senior Democrat on the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"which is also investigating ,","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"`` these investigations must be allowed to continue","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"without interference . ''","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"Republican lawmakers mostly did not to comment .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Flynn 's agreement","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"to cooperate with prosecutors ,","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"which he signed Thursday ,","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"appeared to have come together swiftly .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"A friend of Flynn 's , Robert `` Rocky '' Kempenaar , said","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"the retired general expressed `` anger '' at a dinner","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"the two of them shared in their home state of Rhode Island","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"that his son had been drawn into Mueller 's investigation .","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"`` He was pissed off , ''","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"Kempenaar said of his friend .","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"`` He said","depth":16},{"id":145,"text":"he would n't cooperate with the prosecutor .","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"He was mad","depth":17},{"id":147,"text":"that they were trying to drag his son into it .","depth":17},{"id":148,"text":"He thought","depth":17},{"id":149,"text":"that was dirty . ''","depth":17},{"id":150,"text":"But on Friday morning , Flynn arrived at the federal courthouse in Washington","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"wearing a dark suit with a blue and white striped tie","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"and took a different course .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"He gave short answers to U.S. District Judge Rudolph Contreras 's questions ;","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"his attorneys ,","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"standing on either side of him ,","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"occasionally put their hands on his back .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"`` \" Mr . Flynn , how do you plead to count one of the information ? ''","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"Contreras asked .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"After the judge accepted his plea ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"Flynn returned to the defendant ' s table ,","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"put on a pair of reading glasses","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"and signed some paperwork","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"before being escorted out of the courthouse by U.S . Marshals .","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"He was released without bail .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"In a written plea agreement , prosecutors said","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Flynn likely faces up to six months in prison under federal sentencing rules , and potentially less","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"if investigators are satisfied with the extent of his cooperation .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"He will not be sentenced","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"until he is finished cooperating .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"Trump fired Flynn in February","depth":5},{"id":171,"text":"after misleading Vice President Mike Pence about his conversations with Russian officials .","depth":6},{"id":172,"text":"Pence publicly announced","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"that Flynn assured him","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"the subject of sanctions","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"the Obama administration imposed on Russia","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"were not raised in his conversations with Kislyak after the election .","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"Authorities","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"who had monitored communications","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"involving foreign diplomats","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"knew","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"that was not the case .","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"The day after Flynn was sacked ,","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"then-FBI director Comey said","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"Trump pressured him to end the bureau ' s criminal investigation .","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"who was himself fired in May ,","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"testified to a Senate panel this year","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"that Trump told him","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"Flynn was \" a good guy \"","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"and that \" I hope you can let this go. \"","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"Comey said","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"he took the remarks as an instruction ,","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"but did not obey it .","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"At a news conference the following day , Trump praised Flynn as `` a wonderful man ''","depth":6},{"id":195,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"he has been treated very , very unfairly by the media ,","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"as I call it ,","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"the fake media in many cases . ''","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":201,"text":"Flynn is 3rd national security adviser","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"charged with crimes","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"committed in White House","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"Mueller ' s investigators have separately been gathering records about Trump ' s decision","depth":8},{"id":205,"text":"to fire Comey .","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"As news of Flynn 's cooperation spread ,","depth":6},{"id":207,"text":"Comey quoted a biblical passage on Twitter :","depth":7},{"id":208,"text":"`` But justice roll down like waters and righteousness like an ever-flowing stream . ''","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"The White House had expressed confidence in recent weeks","depth":7},{"id":210,"text":"that Mueller 's investigation was nearing its end .","depth":7},{"id":211,"text":"Flynn 's cooperation makes that `` extremely unlikely , ''","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"Georgetown University law professor Julie O'Sullivan , a former federal prosecutor , said .","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"Among other things ,","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"there would be little reason","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"for prosecutor to secure Flynn 's help","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"if they were not still pursing other targets .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"`` Mueller would never buy a pig in a poke , ''","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"`` He would not give this cooperation deal","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"if Flynn didn ' t have something","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"to offer . ''","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"Mueller ' s office has already filed charges against Trump ' s former campaign chairman Paul Manafort and an associate , Rick Gates .","depth":6},{"id":224,"text":"Another campaign aide , George Papadopoulos ,","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"that he lied to FBI agents about his contacts with a professor","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"he believed","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"`` had substantial connections to Russian government officials '' during the campaign .","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"The professor offered him `` dirt ''","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"- in the form of thousands of emails -","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"on Trump ' s election opponent , Hillary Clinton .","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"In court filings , prosecutors said","depth":8},{"id":232,"text":"that Papadopoulos had agreed to cooperate with Mueller ' s investigation .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":465,"left":0,"right":464,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":464,"left":401,"right":463,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":401,"left":249,"right":400,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":242,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":236,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":234,"right":235,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":239,"right":240,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":237,"right":238,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":243,"right":247,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":245,"right":246,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":13,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":400,"left":275,"right":399,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":255,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":251,"right":254,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":18,"right":250,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":21,"right":253,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":253,"left":252,"right":24,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":252,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":261,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":257,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":257,"left":256,"right":27,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":258,"right":259,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":264,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":32,"right":263,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":33,"right":262,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":266,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":38,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":39,"right":270,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":270,"left":268,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":40,"right":267,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":399,"left":300,"right":398,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":277,"right":299,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":277,"left":276,"right":47,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":297,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":280,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":48,"right":279,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":279,"left":49,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":283,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":52,"right":282,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":53,"right":281,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":295,"left":286,"right":294,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":284,"right":285,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":288,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":60,"right":287,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":287,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":289,"right":292,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":63,"right":64,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":65,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":66,"right":290,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":290,"left":67,"right":68,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":398,"left":310,"right":397,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":310,"left":71,"right":309,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":309,"left":301,"right":308,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":301,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":305,"right":307,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":78,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":74,"right":303,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":303,"left":302,"right":77,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":302,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"elaborati